extendedInfo.description: Radio 92.9 is THE music station in Boston. We're all about the music.If you like tons of rock music without talk...If you like hearing local music from Boston area bands..If you like intimate, in-studio performances and interviews with your favorite artists on demand...If you want updates on Earthfest, Boston's biggest annual free concert and celebration of the earth ...THIS is the app for you.Stream Radio 92.9 more music and less blah blah blah" from Pearl Jam, Coldplay, Linkin Park, U2, Guns & Roses, Foo Fighters, Mumford & Sons, (Do we need to mention more? Ok...) Dave Matthews Band, Adele, Red Hot Chili Peppers, Nirvana, Stone Temple Pilots, Kings Of Leon, (Got it now? No? Here's a few more) Train, Metallica, Green Day, Cage The Elephant, you get the idea.Watch on-demand exclusive Studio 92.9 performances and interviews with Neon Trees, Ok Go, Gavin Rossdale of Bush, Young The Giant, Cracker, Jet, Airborne Toxic Event, Switchfoot, Chadwick Stokes, Crash Kings; The Kooks, Blue October, Silversun Pickups and, of course, more!Stream "Local 92.9," Boston's only station completely dedicated to artists and bands from the area. Non-stop local music, a local music calendar, and a contact directory of local bands.  Are you still reading? Get downloading and get into the music!Includes Ford SYNC integration - Available in AppLink equipped vehicles, with Ford's voice-activation technology. Control our app with voice commands and listen to the live stream or on demand content through your car.
